title: Head Gravity PRO 2021
description: With its massive sweetspot and its bold new flip design, with a yellow-green fade on one side and a blue-violet fade on the other, the GRAVITY PRO is a modern and dynamic racquet for the aggressive next generation player.

title: Head Speed MP 2021
description: The SPEED MP is slightly lighter than the PRO and provides the silo's chracteristics in an easier-to-handle version for a wide range of players.

title: Head Speed MP 2019
description: It comes with the Graphene 360+ technology, a combination of Graphene 360's energy transfer and innovative spiralfibers for an enhanced flex and clean impact feel as well as a 16/19 string pattern for enhanced spin during fast rallies.

title: Head Radical MP
description: Slightly lighter than its bigger brother the RADICAL PRO, the RADICAL MP is designed for the versatile all-court tournament player, with a perfect blend of power, control and spin.

title: Head Radical PRO
description: With a vibrant and daring new design that illustrates its modernity, the RADICAL PRO supplies the perfect blend of power, control and spin for the versatile, all-court and advanced tournament player.

title: Head Extreme MP
description: Generate extreme spin and power with the EXTREME MP, which has been refreshed with a new design, and upgraded with innovative Graphene 360+ technology for enhanced flex and clean impact feel.

title: Head Instinct MP
description: The INSTINCT MP provides effortless high performance and comfort for the advanced tournament player, now with a new design, and the innovative Graphene 360+ technology for enhanced flex and clean impact feel.

title: Head Prestige MP
description: The PRESTIGE MP provides the perfect precision to the experienced player who wants extra control in their long and fast swings.

title: Head Prestige PRO
description: The PRESTIGE PRO is made for the technical tour player who needs a precise racquet that is right to the point.

title: Head Attitude PRO
description: This racquet will make sure that your first steps on the tennis court won't be your last. Pre-strung, the ATTITUDE PRO model provides easier handling and maneuverability.

title: Head Challenge PRO
description: The CHALLENGE PRO, the slightly heavier model compared to the CHALLENGE MP, provides the perfect mix of power and control to the competitive club player.
